item.title: Artists Pay Tribute To Late David Bowie (10+ Pics)
item.description:
Artists Pay Tribute To Late David Bowie (10+ Pics)

The world lost another star yesterday with the passing of David Robert Jones, also known as David Bowie. The 69-year-old died just two days after his birthday and the release of his latest album, Blackstar. We've decided to make an open list from the artistic tributes to Bowie that have been popping up all over the Internet.

item.title: Self-folding material helps the lazy with origami
item.description:
Self-folding material helps the lazy with origami

For the first time, scientists have developed a smart material that can be programmed multiple times to fold itself into complex shapes - without being melted down first. That means that a short flash of heat can trigger the rubbery polymer to fold itself into an origami bird and then into a boat, following another blast of heat.
